metadata.title: Maxbyc Women's Winter Waterproof Warm Mid-Length Puffer Jacket Parka With Hood
features: Unique fabric and lining: The fabric is laminated with thickened PU membrane, and the waterproof and windproof grades can reach 4500mm and 50mm/s respectively, so it can keep dry in light rain or wind and snow. The lining is made of comfortable and soft plush lining to keep you It also stays warm in cold weather.
Thoughtful Design: Full zip and snap closure, adjustable waist and hood cords, stretch windproof cuffs, everything is designed to keep you warm in cold weather.
Practical features: Two deep pockets can hold mobile phones, cards and other items, which are not easy to slip off. The mid-length is designed for a slim fit and keeps your thighs warm.
Using Occasion: This windproof and waterproof women's jacket is perfect for casual and winter outdoor activities.
